name: Diaboromon
effect: [Security] At the end of the battle, you may play 1 [Diaboromon] Token without paying its memory cost. (Diaboromon Tokens are level 6 white Digimon with a memory cost of 14, 3000 DP, and Mega/Unknown/Unidentified traits.)[Opponent's Turn] All of your [Diaboromon] gain ＜Blocker＞. (When an opponent's Digimon attacks, you may suspend this Digimon to force the opponent to attack it instead.)
